snippet.title: Mythlands: Dragon Racing - Game for PC and Oculus Rift
snippet.description:
The first teaser for a project I've been working on in the past few months is here!

For more details about the game, visit http://themythlands.com 
Help me fund the project https://igg.me/at/dragon-racing/x/4604601

For news and updates:
https://www.facebook.com/MythlandsDragonRacing
https://twitter.com/mythlands
https://www.instagram.com/MythlandsDragonRacing
or subscribe for our newsletter here - http://eepurl.com/dBcteL

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Developed with Unreal Engine for PC and Oculus Rift
